snippet.title: Holy Potatoes! What the Hell?! Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Holy Potatoes! What the Hell?! is a whacky hell-themed cooking management sim where you take on the role of a chef in an Afterlife populated by potatoes!
Play our demo on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/664320/Holy_Potatoes_What_the_Hell/
